		Microsoft_AzureSmallText1: "Scalability: Microsoft Azure offers high scalability, allowing businesses to easily scale their resources up or down as needed. This enables them to save costs and optimize the performance of their applications.",
		Microsoft_AzureSmallText2: "Flexibility: Azure supports a variety of programming languages, operating systems, frameworks, and tools, providing developers and businesses with the flexibility to use the most suitable technologies for their specific requirements.",
